{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775842394189,"sessionID":"ses_2878d122affe8iCJXTULzVGdMY","part":{"id":"prt_d7873d38200114Hr19xzA4RHCO","messageID":"msg_d78735ef6001Dm2qMBJOQfFCrM","sessionID":"ses_2878d122affe8iCJXTULzVGdMY","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-bdfc39ca835b4149bb2e1c941acbadee","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/workloadmanager/router.go","content":"package workloadmanager\n\nimport \"github.com/go-chi/chi/v5\"\n\n// Router wraps chi.Router to provide a simplified routing interface.\ntype Router struct {\n\tchi.Router\n}\n\n// NewRouter creates a new Router instance with chi.NewRouter().\nfunc NewRouter() *Router {\n\tr := chi.NewRouter()\n\treturn &Router{Router: r}\n}\n\n// RegisterHandlers registers multiple handlers on the router.\n// Each handler's Register method is called to set up routes.\nfunc (r *Router) RegisterHandlers(handlers ...Handler) {\n\tfor _, h := range handlers {\n\t\th.Register(r.Router)\n\t}\n}"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/recovery.go\">\nERROR [4:2] \"fmt\" imported and not used\n</diagnostics>\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/workloadmanager/server.go\">\nERROR [18:22] undefined: Handler\nERROR [30:29] undefined: Handler\nERROR [37:53] undefined: Handler\n</diagnostics>\n\nLSP errors detected in this file, please fix:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/workloadmanager/router.go\">\nERROR [18:47] undefined: Handler\n</diagnostics>","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_baili